{"hash":"dba4df3083778d400479dfdd020ec321dc5376cc","data":{"tags":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"Technical writing","title":"Technical writing","path":"/tag/technical-writing/"}},{"node":{"id":"Project Management","title":"Project Management","path":"/tag/project-management/"}},{"node":{"id":"Product Management","title":"Product Management","path":"/tag/product-management/"}},{"node":{"id":"Mindfulness & Mental Health","title":"Mindfulness & Mental Health","path":"/tag/mindfulness-and-mental-health/"}},{"node":{"id":"Front-end development","title":"Front-end development","path":"/tag/front-end-development/"}}]},"subjects":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"Speedtest Custom","title":"Speedtest Custom","path":"/subject/speedtest-custom/"}},{"node":{"id":"NinjaTrader","title":"NinjaTrader","path":"/subject/ninja-trader/"}},{"node":{"id":"Multi-threaded programming","title":"Multi-threaded programming","path":"/subject/multi-threaded-programming/"}},{"node":{"id":"JavaScript","title":"JavaScript","path":"/subject/java-script/"}},{"node":{"id":"DirectX","title":"DirectX","path":"/subject/direct-x/"}},{"node":{"id":"Day trading","title":"Day trading","path":"/subject/day-trading/"}},{"node":{"id":"CSS3/HTML5","title":"CSS3/HTML5","path":"/subject/cs-s3-htm-l5/"}},{"node":{"id":"Browser Networking","title":"Browser Networking","path":"/subject/browser-networking/"}},{"node":{"id":".NET-C#","title":".NET-C#","path":"/subject/net-c/"}}]},"doc":{"content":"<h1 id=\"documentation\"><a href=\"#documentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Documentation</h1>\n<h2 id=\"learn-how-to-integrate-my-workflow-and-enable-instant-support-for-your-stakeholders\"><a href=\"#learn-how-to-integrate-my-workflow-and-enable-instant-support-for-your-stakeholders\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Learn how to integrate my workflow and enable instant support for your stakeholders</h2>\n<p>So, you've got some technical debt. You plan to do something a